name: Ed-tech Learning App UI Design Kit
description:
Ed-kit a learning App UI kit consisting of 53 screens UX-friendly design.

The application design made in Figma using auto layout, components and variants, allowing you to quickly edit screens and create new ones. Made with Free Google font.

The design system has equipped typography, color styles, iconography, components and many others.

Ed-kit gives you well organized symbols and layers

with clear structure.
